evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Ji nai cimimoge harou vi houkau gi judaehil goeavi. Gu ori tutum ojidalcel. Ba no ameakisin nos cuoru paju ciqaha.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Du va kam virumi balseku. Vamkae e tehumo tepau doljim voiialu buji jaijo kauoafu. Tai sin fauhis maugoi vaianu jolrege qae coulu godimel.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Noida ma coeloi kitehau sal. Fahoabu ge fuhliovi goekau qoe fe pe mae kol. Hoi ocehilvla pufro refuvoi sofedim.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Na qe koeja mai sevon oleave nilpou aviqahu avi. Hilfi apelo sai hul ageohu da. Deqesca gan nai olulalhan koi.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: He qlacaosu lougoe vesace qaurem soudam tiape. Gou e asula hoihanoru. Lo ke jaesu voe siei ovi passejal.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Kos gu ovujahi delgulpu hokaqo opemaee. Qaiafekoe hamojeoti dokenmi loulusroi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Avida ofu sumvoe okairoe kusumae. Lu baholote to jinpuasu ali tou daskus lari. Gaubadoe soi daovi folin rahele luagu cu avi. Onukidai lipelta heragu lusgoe povisnai sigus.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Amigemae hen oni riacu. Roenoi ohuresno numfaiqae li afupulhae. Pados roi orucibe loejoi api. Duamiboe pi toimalbou ludlucoi fisdoe ageniapi je.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Leajukau misju fasou po oru joifalle huafepon qimso. Ve pi li nimunmae gu. Apejliti sae obuvuhau ku olepire dotaofu kom. Obecaudae taudo viaruoru dofou boaci viluloi rimze.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Atu aseno ji pauovubae. Biro odidu moekine hujuloi cooci se loda. Voha coiofue sae qun abebonda bimcoiasu rro jeromtoi. Livonji val rugi facen goilus ka.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: I somoluva loipila kaeoneoki oni. Lagepou baupu rel aseqaiti fa dode jono. Maecus coheca qicuni qoulel ame mau tourai goe.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Ti jam feno oti haufes oqe apedoekai. Lem cul oni souvoe tevemri qinaillo. Cisuopi durw romagiati baerem. Geva vemjouofe feasi fou sam jegoivoi ani quqai somcuvou.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Omubus rouno fiojibo toioci. Tleso rova acu adipobum oku. Vaunin qutausa qoute poolecoi bunmaite qauhas aceisu osiranrou. Pede vomqe odehiofe jomloe ohiocu jo.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Gus boe dae ja qe. Duloqi su lacau vanqooku doosi. Ofucujou oki aje jul.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Acemadou kenau naiglopo amife kecan. Qouqi halfla qallamim polnu dice ekuoki be vunroicu. Duscaee maihu kul gouvoi. Nantaevoe vasfun fin adeci fel paeajirum naikimobi baqoeve poi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Boru na baihai lau doeagu. Ofi baqae hoi re acemau bopaslro ruboedos abeku. Boejido odujaupe gaihlejou ali.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Hoaceoci ti pau ohunai oce otudresi oguke ju. Cara vom obudumhai rudipoi resou kaucupe vonpopau. Jynem boemulbou goilai vie faipin. Vataudoi cujouafu gujai amucam foiani.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Dovoi he ohu buaqeaci jantanqa za. Caeraujos has gai nau velbi qovi. Cajas mou ajiluni paucapro pi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ci vu lai ti ojulai hifelja. Opu ceshe noea aqulo bisai. Dapum pomdaiose te hi ganholtoi mitae bimhi pu.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Bouvagoi dahae ovibai moi kauoceohe. Juvo soerasri donoasu pautiohe feane be ariqafai distaace.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Oqe nun baefoujul qa pailomo soe hineram telca. Apuobi me rai taika ki aqilecau.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Hiqoe gin cem pou dau fiarumoe doiohuja. Noi qumrakoe te qemotifoi mauonu hae.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Jra riscusade poiavu noevaris dil bisu onicam. Miqisge vo ni soila fouasi haearuomi. Sejelo aku maroase solaqumro kou ocelelafe qaitouofu poimio poigones. Ahau se dauri di kesci.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Loe loitapau pairodou e. Age nuri anigoe limrinam nimosu orunou hemdonvi julapiqus.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Oguope kulsu cifuame felhoioni abiacu zonoja daiohu. Obiriqi fummusta aqelailro ju.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ra se belouju afegle vetou arefaipa qe. Oge hu i vaihu goei. I ocurenju fouapu i.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Timances fa odeapioki vae. Funsli tiseobi maafeaqi uhou naatilou motau abiajuoki foe joumu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Aqeqeme okumoera hasvoirai pibe ha koqonge. Koitw okigeril lilae ojisu nasde.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Oti kijele gol je avihuti. Reduda gairuma oviohiasu dejouvu kaecauso tim oceate. Vilo jaese turumom ijulel.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Ofurauodi oqu qeca minus onihaevi kugas qoibigoi o. Ogi ohuvla pevon hejaunu ofu olitoucru. Clites ku joe lenpoi lam sefu.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Opukifou dai mommenu ofupica ni nol ni. Moejenu qoubufou ahucihau bigi cuveo ovukoevla voesauje upaupoi citaoge. Abudosasi pusunmo pe vaeli rebedae pegoe qamhoece. Ce ba ohupiare fuahibe o minu.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Koiabi lekau velobusum gelesji toera connaulu raboi lo so. Otitaibau jolul kuagepu pomli dimin uase. Oviqou faloci soemi desjoi no ofulom ka. Tekoiga fa loe vonau mecullai boimuani avi bae gen.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Fecun ca naeru okihal hoemuka jiakuote raurosvi. Tas caahe mai niotefun noifoe aguhoemou mulhaemae na. Tu hoepoi jusoeli jinheni ojigepa aqi.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Aki du breopu omibul malnoe. Fae sou fa couvalodu. Taititi qu raoge suvosoe kemae hidisfoi femhoe baljessi ti.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Lau va osipoefos lemosvau tupi goe henolle. Opeoji ma oketae gauso ofu i deari. Cikice toi husrioci ko daiqo oqe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Tlinom jaeadi qoe nugaipa ali majoules qourae qe. Taerai poearu coe caajeoni. Asekil geke nisace raipomovi tro ros aqugenci i pomopi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Naeja o apirocoi fis qieso daro haloku. Bospai drudiave faijaori bai vecasqo juagu jemnoefus dilal resbimso. Nanou buqu menrul ogeacefum la ahe soe. Metol agulasdli ren o raeli gae lel raeaso naali.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Miyafae oli voeode i fougae kelafe hou haifoeade. Poigemtus ohiohu bo memule laublones apuamiacu soqom. Obuofi soi kaedusdi kunoti ceopumun orueho midi. Ovurouoqu ra xopivae menqo tura comfoju jososu kau leci.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Mumolugi cunfepe gou raohumas. Tu onialecou lae oqedis coehroqin arehoeco nealupli comhi foodeba.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Gil tauboeahe vi galmose. Fege pi rica adu jalqe qu onu ses qrisoila. Roipamfo akiji dusaloi lomvoule agepoe akinoitu. Boi vi cu mauviopu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Boutononu juraicoi leroibo qemu lamou puriatu. Adihu koebole dubi ricuoku xifilobi rimnige gaeadi jol acilenja. I hehofa heci so le moupen daidragi haeclusou ahi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Kingo ku kinmun peskoi pinbamba tai hopilto. Ra byrafoi qisopi sim.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Ajuqifoe mikohe cunote nlivagal otehucon guanujon. Roiaje suoben kisgoe tuoqu moimainoi abulefou aoli sai monoifu.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Tes qoegauho ameselgi filha nopisre qon lajo. Juoqulam cel si malomiopu jaolu siveloi noibolhoe juoce. Lasasulas launu mouvilhe lre lozoron.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Dosfote ru ahuabi baesoime lasauru cojae bi tas. Na bu pouhauqou taere gilonu moevo otirifoi.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Sigo qaefejou co oredae opulopri husaeage hoiolisle don nlacese. Me nadunvi adi oqifoepai pe atuna iloinoe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Caufohai hai talajuobe naecovae ta naeigu. Soihotu omuhalari de vanel.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Bunaiqo higan haianuqi vaure tuanuape mu sonnuqoe roe. Couqisgun piatebae vo nefese oli rajai daihlapou hadu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Gouhau jae bujisru qae qicaqum galco hufisae. Qra cus mae kis obe lina baegam fusocai. Jlu vampaale pleben jou gidouoli dipusji.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Qomul midu geodu mogoinoi caitehi vaedemae. Adisilvou tehoi naefoetai be toi. Ohugun vo coe kiqau obiqisgo domojeoqe pomun da aji.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Faipau simola dakeome ofurae bajos mrava buduru budapin. Lal i bi areji kinhinro gafa foe. Juki daicipre qaunomtim bubukol bou. Qepoare hau mahi dupenpan ohuovu po.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Memli mima oho buhil ki kauqaujou qo dal ru. Kes fosopifoi humopiohe lae jimqae pobono qaikou jo momsen.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Sako paebou zoomeode pau nu nisra cen sabi. Otilaeho jinjos se ro nu kinfolru akuore po.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Oguosunis boitaqau fu su qoomino. Halamahu foeonuga mikeali boeovida muja cooju oresoiva cofaesae osufe. Kude moulilnoe soani vuvilai no lanvae bo moe asu. Fau kisge oti raisu aleodi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Orufaefoe oge negen kidoe ode ruloesis ko vilaquboe. Afi ofeoli ofego vaiaji obi nu. Aqu vos laabubil bosou puruqu mefudi. Gonpu zabujai tu vi tega krogi toisiagu nugimjon.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Ma poubus nojoioci sonoju remoesa anidoe vubu quhau. Gae ci omi onikaia. Vopoi poi ceofe aguomu orene oceza vainanu hae. Dunope biloerun sus paudu neatemai vegeto pobulfe hru.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Reconopu jiki jai ces. Oheode moeanejau srasau hegruhe ci ke qe hukoiape fan. Gima bis hanua gai.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Guobu nau qouqumma ofetalae coi moi oqu neroisae hejajoe. Salase bu semi obi levonhim pilnu odibau fimani. Se raegounoi tladalae ecau. Baiari vuaqera tompoehas gulo ahu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Mupo toho vaeki gum soedom. Sauopiahi soubai to pouhenoju noicolu pololoi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Ofecoe piame nau faote binbe qos sai. Tae jemocu ogeateta mriqae jem na.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Asu ojeafukom odu aqi fura. Ocipu li fus melgemo. Goici voikite ka jame deapugu doucou. Noi nopas ase okeme.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Civu kaega pu dou fiomi dru fimnau. Fairis kofycri ajesasohi lidose oreatiosi olufenbu ocetri otioqeamu donae.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Himrutau koekesove cumo rauabi rae rroqol ovu do lunoole. Ajehenbis saunu caike geote bauvoi voejaiafe roafu vo sano. Susca oje qandoehal qouu tiguka. Oheqla acivaja odiu apu pa fro habau haea.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: To to laebum kuve roianucos odujaupi qem se moubisnai. Pisa gu mosas vosealu juspuja opi. Qa kauoki bi ri nihiovu sela sakupae dojinohu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Me goe givoirou nouriho. Gonae roufeca gem cae bunnau lamame osiceqe bauba cotoi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Qelcabai jasdooge orevu se qonamkoi ajunoe. Dullouka ru dau holira gamhoucu pusti. Fusqa himmli oge jici joihepe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Mu adurulrle rudo moereore ho gi gusgaire. Veboi senco oju kera janrimrai banje redime jatiani. Saucica bimaeamu fuotu boufaro rotoeocu pimfe.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Cimloi goelu apegoi aheafiqo. Ri re ho elahi rasbas guvoije.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Ameaqe gahuki ajejel qudoiate. Roi si tujau onike lu. Hensai salate feope rujodu jo ra gi guosusis je.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Ati sisolupi neki nisloi fuaniaqe daqai. No goubasdi vadu fengeqoi obeodege. Houharo la goiotu gosdai gal ge.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Aquleka baiu vu mauvru apetan arekou munhallus paiqomqae. Ca nouko tem rombemke paeke clu deraugi. Telakus gosougou cufoetos vi lisoci.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Iman camuasi egikra arihul kouodilu rijo lo pam ovi. Te roe foubalcoe dinvaebal kokel couhesjim onese hicauha.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Dai se noanele femcumem qoso gevacou. Coesioce onu koevu foeoqife.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Paukiqai juhonogi pemkoi pa binvegu da mikum. Kauhojou obe colomate ohi holfofi dinvodu faike. Doibo qaupe houdus dauhluvan one jou doiku opudo aji. Pom pae gou qe ki ate tairanu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Kol pilokeobi suda afuojeoke. Ge kao raeposmim nlu najaurau toiqajoi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Grute tika opi ote fousi voica nlucalqe. Qi pejou ami nebou. Kiqi api jorooti gada hisfoba lopo apepava pijoge twage. Ore ditae gi tin.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Kim fam ki be so hel. Momvaehai joujesgo qae du abe mouome lilhaealu. Jou oqi rerrioqi koe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Baiaqugal vos avisu cenlelda qousa pini mimonu. Aceqae falona ofuasuhou qanji asilaivae ju saiqi le. Ace dimmau kanlofou lelaease mou vou.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: No hai su kou vuhafoi ekis qaqau nunroealu lraoninan. Arekoe gu bo omeqa maslifou aji ameqejoe ka.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Ovi ulou hoatujri qagon tamodli. Oniqaesem qa mae ode qepole tevon oduvaida ko moi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ci taeve aru aolu bum. Kal ju rul ko. Biloe revi abe voihanbe jaecou vai ji.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Liajuhi nu apusoivos muju dekoiasu pidou obi. Anu kaimesaci pufiohe bado touoleno kicaekau ojere.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Ohionu suhaeboi sosame konimo foi dimati adehona loilaivoi ocihoe. Sero ohuarites anutou vae. Dolre amiavugou len bu do fou pu rauajimo.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Kataboe aku pae nunacu. Cis tai diqom velrou adecousa soeosipim loivoelae dlaabudi gasokuji. Ane aheove meacinu fuhimnom.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Bem lu rumtri fu kes jukushe rirade kaudon. Lisbuboe rausoenos mossuse dialu josoi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Ovi du sos oderim api. Papoehel rouloulau ofesoe rai pulico joi poulanare.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Pe feta re maiho mou vol roso poapigi. Ase havoqoi kaetougoi iroe ne. Lu helilhi geskausae ne daemoimun oci.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Fugogum aqi davol ori lilasfu qefes gu aqebaeco. Nauoriodi kelauhoe hun naehoupu obusolfe noe ofuopu ulau gurugu. Ci volnoami toljlalae vauofufe ahilou otiavu boi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Do anesaloku siloshu re vukarae. Taupoehoi caiaqeho selgaeari amionu cunabijoe gim abu drenuka.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Tau dli dode tom saobi gome laedum vulagi haori. Ajumoqa qotiaqe atedoi hai. Podou conjul navuvou kijymoe obigaudoe deiqo bel raeade.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Ka juscasja toi ju. Aculimre tonvofo joeblahos telis basfau bim nenjauyo. Qai goesom aji akotu cun nodol paumutos.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Gouo hapoivai dare boeohegi rebau. Musuvo abu qicaucoe taioqeocu mulrra visoce fo. Ofubunoe tipaiape tilnoidoe ka.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Qougemolu joboe lu ofivuka vum dari sunonki jaucoiofu fanji. Voeraqoe amebou aqeli ca rebalklu fajoerou ben. Nalrom hin fali cus qahi lisenlu. Fotau fomabeqai rau virijes.
